                                    "keywords": "motivation, some sensors operate by changing their resistance, e.g., temperature sensors in form of thermistors, Wheatstone bridge supports precise measurements, (original) operation principle, resistors R1, R3 and potentiometer R2, fixed but unknown resistor Rx, adjust R2 until there is no current flow through VG"
