                                    "keywords": "Wheatstone Bridge, (original) operation principle, re-draw the circuit (two voltage dividers), formula U5 = U0 * (R1R4 - R3R2) / ((R1 + R2)(R3 + R4)), U0 = 0 => R1R4 = R3R2 => R1/R2 = R3/R4, three Ri are known, hence fourth can be computed"
