                                    "keywords": "Wheatstone Bridge, operation principle for resistance changes R'1 = R1 + ΔR, formula U5 = U0 * vk / ((1 + v + k)(1 + k)), with v = ΔR/R1 and k = R2/R1 = R4/R3"
